{
  "id": 5915984063889408,
  "name": "DeviceOrientation Events permission request API",
  "summary": "Allows web developers to call Device{Motion,Orientation}Event.requestPermission() to ask the user agent for device orientation and motion data to be shared with the page. Those two static methods return a promise that resolves to either \"granted\" or \"denied\" based on whether the user has allowed the user agent to share sensor data with pages.",
